---
---
<section class="intro">
  <div class="inner">
    <div class="headline-block">
      <h2>ヒトが、<br />創造と出会う。</h2>
      <p class="sub">たちが 創造 と出会える世界へ。</p>
    </div>
    <div class="body-block">
      <p>
        たくさんの出会いと、つくる時間に支えられ、<br />
        人に寄り添いながら、心に残る映像と体験を。<br />
        これから、映像をもっと身近に。<br />
        だれもが "創造" と出会える世界へ。
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="badge">
      <div class="badge-ring">
        <span class="num">10</span><span class="th">th</span>
        <span class="label">ANNIVERSARY</span>
        <span class="since-badge">since 2015</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .intro {
    padding: 72px 80px;
    background: #0d0d0d;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }
  .inner {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: auto 1fr auto;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 64px;
  }
  .headline-block { flex-shrink: 0; }
  h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 2.8vw, 2.6rem);
    font-weight: 300;
    color: #fff;
    line-height: 1.55;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }
  .sub {
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
  }
  .body-block p {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 300;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6);
    line-height: 2.1;
  }
  .badge {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
  }
  .badge-ring {
    width: 120px;
    height: 120px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-gold);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 2px;
  }
  .num {
    font-family: var(--font-en);
    font-size: 2.6rem;
    font-weight: 300;
    color: var(--color-gold);
    line-height: 1;
  }
  .th {
    font-family: var(--font-en);
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--color-gold);
    margin-top: -6px;
    align-self: flex-end;
  }
  .label {
    font-family: var(--font-en);
    font-size: 0.5rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    color: var(--color-gold);
    margin-top: 2px;
  }
  .since-badge {
    font-family: var(--font-en);
    font-size: 0.5rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    color: rgba(184,150,90,0.6);
  }
</style>
